text: Georges Wengler (14 November 1918 - 10 May 2004) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1918 births Category:2004 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Luxembourg City
